    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a quintessential driver\u2019s specimen, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanically robust, the dual-VANOS system has been professionally serviced and the rear subframe reinforced, addressing the primary structural concerns of this platform. The factory limited-slip differential provides exceptional power delivery out of corners, while the chassis remains composed under high lateral loads. Though it shows minor cosmetic patina consistent with regular use, the powertrain remains tight and the throttle response is instantaneous. It is an analog performance icon optimized for the spirited driver.",
